cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on egocentric action recognition using RGB and Flow modalities. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with multi-modal fusion of audio and visual data. 
- cs.SD (Sound) and cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing) are also possible categories as the paper deals with audio processing and temporal binding of modalities. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on developing new machine learning algorithms, but rather on applying existing techniques to a specific problem.
